headline: Nymex May oil rises 37 cents, or 0.7%, to close at $50.79 a barrel
Gold drops $9.50, or 0.8%, to settle at $1,193.60/oz
Weak 30-year Treasury auction sparks selloff in the market
Euro falls to 3-week low of $1.0657
Stoxx Europe 600 ends at all-time closing high of 409.15
AMC Entertainment downgraded to neutral from buy at MKM Partners
U.S. wholesale inventories rise 0.3% in February
Alcoa shares drop 2.7%
Bed Bath & Beyond shares fall 3.7%
S&P 500 flat; Nasdaq Composite up 0.1%
